## DISPOSITION — SUPERSEDED [2026-06-21 02:05 ET, conductor]

**Verdict: SUPERSEDED by the terminal strategy-campaign verdict (STATUS 2026-06-21 00:15) + OP-22 "STOP entry-hunting (saturated)".** Not cooked. Rationale:
- The campaign real-fills-tested ~27 strategies across 3 parallel hunts + fleet scorecard + SwjshAK port; **exactly ONE survivor (vwap_continuation, already LIVE).** Continuation did NOT beat reversion; the 0DTE OPTION STRUCTURE (theta/delta/stop-misfire), not the entry signal, is the wall. A new low-VIX bear *continuation* entry is squarely in the killed class.
- This proposes RELAXING the filter_8 VIX-direction gate to chase low-VIX bear days. That contradicts **L93** (the existing bearish read correctly requires the *declining-not-escalating* VIX character — F8 is already regime-aware) and **C5/L154** (high-score + 0-trade + declining-VIX = the engine *correctly abstaining*, not a missed edge).
- The 2026-06-16 0-trade outcome the item cites IS the correct behavior, not a structural blind spot.
- If a future J ruling reopens entry-expansion, re-derive from real ★★★ levels + a fresh A/B; do not resurrect this proxy-era proposal verbatim. Closed per OP-22 compound-don't-accumulate.
